RecordThing.Description:
When a single circuit breaker isn't enough, you need something with more oomph.  That's what the Heavy Circuit Breaker does.
Connect a breaker to two {THING:BusTie} and optionally a {THING:DataBusTie}, using a {THING:ItemScrewdriver}, and the Heavy Breaker can interrupt currents up to 500kW.
The Heavy Circuit Breaker can access any connected {THING:BusTie} including through other Heavy Circuit Breakers or a {THING:Wireway}
